    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bridges having supports comprising a braced framework of timbers, piles, or steelwork usually of considerable height; used for carrying a road or railroad over a depression.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
